entries.femaleVariant: Hey, V. Orbital connections cost an arm and a leg, so I'll just get right to it.
There are more things in heaven and earth, than are dreamt of in my philosophy, right?
I mean, in the end... In the end it was your choice. Your choice to make.
But... Well, you should know it didn't just affect you. It hit your friends, too.
I don't think... I don't think you knew just how many friends you really had.
Maybe we'll see each other again, V. You, me... Jackie.
Until then... Take care.
I know, I know the reading's not as strong without you here, but we haven't seen each other for so long and I... Well, one thing led to another.
You know what I drew? The Chariot, the Lovers and the Sun.
Hah. Looks like you've got a good life ahead of you, out in the Badlands.
Good luck, V. Be free.
I know, I know the reading's not as strong without you here, but we haven't seen each other for so long and I... Well, one thing led to another.

Babe... The world's gonna hear about you.
Go and show Night City what you're made of.
But... Well, I was wondering how you were doing, so I laid out a quick tarot, and... Oh dear...
The Hanged Man. The Magician. The Star.
Those... Those are not good cards, V. They're really bad... Something like death, but not quite.
Take care of yourself, OK? I'll... I hope to hear from you soon.

The Fool. The Moon. The High Priestess. Those, uh... those are bad cards.
